## ğŸ› ï¸ Installation

1. **Clone the repo**:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/sstv-python.git
cd sstv-python
```

2. **Install requirements**:
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

3. **Run the app**:
```bash
streamlit run app.py
```

